emonstrating alignment with these values can enhance your candidacy.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1718281491402\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q10.Are there opportunities for career growth at Oracle?<br><\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. Yes, Oracle encourages career development through internal mobility, professional development programs, mentorship, and training opportunities.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Oracle is hiring freshers and experienced graduates in 2024. It begins with an online application, followed by initial screenings and phone interviews to shortlist suitable candidates. Depending on the position, candidates may complete technical assessments before moving on to in-depth interviews, including technical, behavioral, and managerial evaluations. This thorough approach ensures that Oracle recruits &#8230; <a title=\"Oracle Recruitment Process 2024- Step-by-Step Process\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/oracle-recruitment-process\/\" aria-label=\"More on Oracle Recruitment Process 2024- Step-by-Step Process\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":12120,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1087,42],"tags":[1093,1095,1094],"class_list":["post-12115","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-oracle","category-interview-prep","tag-oracle-recruitment-process-2024","tag-oracle-recruitment-process-for-experienced","tag-oracle-recruitment-process-for-freshers","generate-columns","tablet-grid-50","mobile-grid-100","grid-parent","grid-33"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/12115"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],